Source: atri-main
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: AtriOS contributors <none@example.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 13), libc6-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.0

Package: atri-main
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Offline userspace daemon for AtriStation LED matrix and ring
 atri-main replaces the cloud-dependent maind from Yandex Station 2 firmware.
 It drives the local SPI framebuffer, the 24 RGB ring LEDs, reacts to input
 events, and plays offline animations. No network, cloud, Alice or WebRTC
 code is included.
